{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act32side", "eventName": "水晶箭行動", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "CR-5", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "消防通道", "storyInfo": "先遭雷內爾數次耍弄，又受到來自聯合政府的壓力，山窮水盡的上尉發覺前途無望，終於下定決心，制定了殘忍的計劃。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_20_G07", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$tech_intro", "key": "$tech_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_207", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_207", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_198_1#1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "布克，有事嗎？", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#1"}, {"id": 16, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_207", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "坎黛拉女士，上尉先生好像是坐不住了。", "name": "市長保鏢"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_207"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_198_1#2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "被雷內爾耍了那麼多次，他現在才坐不住嗎？", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#2"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_207", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們的人遞消息過來，說是他打算動用武力來搞定那片社區。", "name": "市長保鏢"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_207"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_198_1#3", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在我的地界上動武，他哪裡來的膽子？", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#3"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_207", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聯合政府內有人支持他的行動，現在他有權調遣城內所有聯合政府的軍事力量。", "name": "市長保鏢"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_207"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_198_1#1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些傢伙，手伸得越來越長了……", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_207", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們是否要採取行動阻止？", "name": "市長保鏢"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_207"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_198_1#1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "暫且不動吧。社區那群人隨心所欲，常常和市政府唱反調。要是他們真能將那裡的事情解決乾淨，也算是幫了我一個忙。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過你也要時刻盯著，馬特奧生性短視又貪婪，手握這麼大的權力，我不信他不會動些歪腦筋。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_207", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "此外，坎黛拉女士，幾天後的克里斯達爾藝術館的開幕式您打算去嗎？", "name": "市長保鏢"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_207"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_198_1#2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，那也是個愛惹是生非的啊……我不去了，派人把賀禮送到就行。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#2"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_207", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我先下去了。", "name": "市長保鏢"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_207"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_198_1#1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等，還有一件事我需要埃內斯托去做，你記得告訴他。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "48_g11_deluxeroom_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.5}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_dia_street_intro", "key": "$m_dia_street_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crwddiscuss_outside", "loop": "true", "channel": "1", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雷內爾，你還記得我嗎？幾年前我們見過一面。", "name": "殷勤的投資商"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "雷內爾", "content": "您是……等等，別提醒我，我一定能想起來。"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "雷內爾", "end": "true", "content": "諾里斯先生，對嗎？三年前我們一起競標過一尊來自米諾斯的雕像。", "joined": "您是……等等，別提醒我，我一定能想起來。諾里斯先生，對嗎？三年前我們一起競標過一尊來自米諾斯的雕像。"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我對你優秀的記憶力有深刻的印象，那天晚上你一直在談論那尊雕像，從它的創作者到幾個經手的收藏家，你竟然都記得。", "name": "殷勤的投資商"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，不輕易忘記……確實，算是我的優點之一了。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#1$1"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這麼長時間不見，你的變化可真大，褪去了青澀，越發有你父親的風範了。", "name": "殷勤的投資商"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只可惜他離開得太早，不能看見我正在做的一切。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#1$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別太傷感，當孩子做出一番超越父輩的偉業，就算父親無法得見，他也必定會為自己的孩子感到自豪。", "name": "殷勤的投資商"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呵……但願他真的會吧。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#9$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_176", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "科瓦爾斯基先生，我剛剛一直在找您呢。", "name": "諂媚的收藏家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘿，切蒂，最近還好嗎？樓底下的展館裡剛剛到了一幅伊比利亞的濕壁畫，去年一整年你都在四處奔波，收集這些傑作。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#9$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_176", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那都是去年的事了，今天我打算盡可能多地買入那些來自炎國的水墨畫。", "name": "諂媚的收藏家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "想不到你們那裡的投資風向轉變得這麼快。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#1$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這就是雷內爾你不知道了，哪裡是投資風向變得快，是我們切蒂先生的心變得快。", "name": "殷勤的投資商"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……這話聽來有趣。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#10$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）他今年新換了一位太太，那位女士很喜歡水墨畫。", "name": "殷勤的投資商"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_176", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然你說到這個，有些事我就直白講了，科瓦爾斯基先生。", "name": "諂媚的收藏家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那些濕壁畫我想盡快出手，不知道您有沒有門路，瑪麗她很討厭凱瑟琳留下的藏品。", "name": "諂媚的收藏家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "應該有些辦法，我會盡量試試的。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#10$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_176", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別謙虛了，您可是斯特凡·科瓦爾斯基的兒子，您父親當年只用了不到半個月就將我手中所有悉數……", "name": "諂媚的收藏家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.5}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "-100,0", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.5}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1", "posfrom": "200,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 2.0}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "1", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "100,0", "duration": 2.0}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，不好意思，雷內爾先生，我沒注意到您站在這裡。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_176", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你這女人怎麼回事，看不到三個大活人站在這裡嗎？", "name": "諂媚的收藏家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "諸位，她是我新聘來的保鏢，我之後會教訓她的。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#1$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請問您現在需要換件衣服嗎？", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然了，這些酒黏在身上真的很難受，失陪了，諸位。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#1$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_ltroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$darkness_03_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "多虧你那杯酒，再有一個人圍過來我就要窒息了。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#1$1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不用謝，該做的。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#3$1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還以為你今天不會來這裡，明天社區的木偶戲劇就要正式開演，事情不該很多？", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#1$1"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們的合約還沒有結束。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "多麼令人感動的契約精神啊……結束後呢，你們打算去哪裡？", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#9$1"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你背上……？", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#5$1"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦，你說那些傷疤？沒什麼，一些叛逆的代價罷了。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#1$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……等合約結束後，我們打算離開多索雷斯，繼續尋找我們失蹤的隊友。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#7$1"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然這樣，可能我們也不會有什麼機會再見了。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#1$1"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我這樣任性的雇主，要不是有合約約束著，你早就一走了之了吧。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#9$1"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也算不上什麼省心的僱員，你能忍受我到現在，也讓我覺得很驚訝。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#3$1"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#10$1"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝你對我們的幫助，希望以後你一切都好，雷內爾先生。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不會還帶了東西給我吧？", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#9$1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，一張唱片，是社區裡一位歌手賣給我的。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我好像對上面這個名字有點印象，哦，想起來了，他去年出了一首二十七分鐘的歌來罵我。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#9$1"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這我倒是不知道……我只是單純覺得你可以聽一聽裡面的歌。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒關係，不用緊張，我已經報復回去了。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#1$1"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你幹了什麼？", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#5$1"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我從他前公司那裡買了不少他創作的歌曲的版權，然後交給了他最痛恨的口水歌流行樂團改編。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#9$1"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……專輯我留在這裡，你要是想聽可以聽聽，不想聽就算了。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#7$1"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_offce", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$mist_intro", "key": "$mist_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1210_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……是的，他的確在幾天前我打電話給他的時候……扯了電話線。", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#2$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我懇請您再給我一些時間，我會想辦法拿到那塊地皮的……我們的開發計劃一定能按時進行。", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#2$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先生，您知道的，我一向對您忠心耿耿，我並非對此事不上心，確實是事情有些棘手。", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#2$1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "捏著開發權的商人不願意配合，來軟的來硬的都沒有用。", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#2$1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "直接從社區入手我們也嘗試過了，但那裡的人都是些硬角色，我們已經吃過虧了。", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#2$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1210_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不、不是藉口，情況當真是這樣，而且……而且聯合政府內似乎有另一批人在為雷內爾撐腰，我不敢妄動。", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#6$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1210_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是屬下無能，沒能查出來他們的來歷，所以斗膽問問您，是否……有什麼線索？例如……到底是誰想從您手中分去多索雷斯這塊蛋糕？", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#2$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，我不是質疑您在聯合政府內的地位，只是有這樣一個可能。", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#2$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1210_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您要我不顧一切放手去做……這、這能行嗎？如果真的因此得罪了什麼人……", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#6$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1210_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好，有您這句話作保證，我就不擔心了，我一定不辜負您的期望。", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#1$1"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_telephone"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1271_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "上尉，難道就連那位先生也不知道那些人的來歷嗎？", "name": "帶隊的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1271_1#1$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1210_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他不知道，不過他也不在意。他將多索雷斯城內的最高指揮權授予我，示意我盡快解決此事。", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#1$1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1271_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "坎黛拉那邊？", "name": "帶隊的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1271_1#1$1"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1210_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那位先生說他會搞定。", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#3$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1271_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果那位先生願意全力幫忙，那問題一定能解決，但您……您看起來怎麼反而不開心？", "name": "帶隊的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1271_1#1$1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1210_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你仔細想想，什麼樣的屬下需要上級全力幫忙才能成事？", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#8$1"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1271_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "深受信任的？", "name": "帶隊的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1271_1#1$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1210_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼，當然是沒本事的屬下……", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#8$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我原本想靠著做成開發計劃好好在那位先生面前表現一番，這下好了，恐怕現在他只覺得我是個等著他來擦屁股的蠢貨。", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#8$1"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1271_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等拿到那塊地皮，事情辦成了，說不定他就不會計較了。", "name": "帶隊的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1271_1#1$1"}, {"id": 225, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1210_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我可賭不起一個說不定，他身邊有個年輕人最近職位升得飛快，聽說正要被派到這裡來。", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#3$1"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1210_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是不想被替代，我光拿到地皮可不夠，還得有些額外的“功績”。", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#1$1"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1271_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是有什麼想法了嗎？", "name": "帶隊的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1271_1#1$1"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1210_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，而且想了有段時間了，雷內爾三番五次把我當傻子耍，我要是不回敬些什麼，豈不是太廢了。", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#8$1"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果能連同那座藝術館也一併吞下就好了……", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#8$1"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1210_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "離他那場開幕式還有一兩天，在這麼短的時間內……", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#1$1"}, {"id": 236, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1210_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來只也能辦得狠一點，走最險的那條路了。", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#3$1"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_20_G08", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper1"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_486_espumo_1#7", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "古怪……實在是太古怪……", "name": "龍舌蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorknockquite"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "埃內斯托，我看你庫房的燈亮著，你還沒睡嗎？", "name": "空爆"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_486_espumo_1#1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿萊塔？請進吧。", "name": "龍舌蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}, {"id": 259, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_282_catap_1#10$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_486_espumo_1#1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_282_catap_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還在忙社區的事？這幾天確實大家都忙壞了。", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_282_catap_1#10$1"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_486_espumo_1#1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，要真是社區的事就好了，我做起來也有熱情……是有些不得不還的人情債啊。", "name": "龍舌蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_282_catap_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是上次尋找藥品時欠的人情？有什麼我能幫忙的嗎？", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_282_catap_1#8$1"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_486_espumo_1#5", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "想什麼呢？不是，是些私人的事情。", "name": "龍舌蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#5"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_282_catap_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老兄，有事別一個人扛，有需要我的地方就及時說。", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_282_catap_1#10$1"}, {"id": 276, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_486_espumo_1#1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放心，不是什麼大事，你早點休息吧。", "name": "龍舌蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_282_catap_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……算了，你這人一向這樣，什麼事都藏在心裡，臉上是一點也看不出來，別人想幫都幫不了。", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_282_catap_1#2$1"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_486_espumo_1#5", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你真的是多想了，阿萊塔。", "name": "龍舌蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#5"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_282_catap_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哪裡是多想，你一直這麼行事，別人就只會這麼想你……我走了，你記得早點休息。", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_282_catap_1#7$1"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "100,0", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "200,0", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_486_espumo_1#7", "posfrom": "200,0", "posto": "200,0"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼……", "name": "龍舌蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓你幫忙和拖你下水可不是一回事，這可怪不了我啊。", "name": "龍舌蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}, {"id": 294, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper1"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奇怪，這麼大量的炸藥怎麼一進城就消失得無影無蹤呢？", "name": "龍舌蘭"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "二十八號，有一批……次月三日，又有一批……", "name": "龍舌蘭"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "同時期還有一批釀酒的原材料運來，借運酒的幌子送進來的？不，不是，路線對不上，四個檢查點，不可能不被發現。", "name": "龍舌蘭"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper1"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_486_espumo_1#3", "posfrom": "200,0", "posto": "200,0"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "除非……那些貨物根本不會有人檢查。", "name": "龍舌蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#3"}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很貴重，沒人敢妄動？", "name": "龍舌蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#3"}, {"id": 306, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_486_espumo_1#7", "posfrom": "200,0", "posto": "200,0"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……奢侈品？名酒？", "name": "龍舌蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可……那些都不夠貴重。在現在的多索雷斯，動輒幾千萬一億個的該不會是……", "name": "龍舌蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（嚥口水）", "name": "龍舌蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不……我得去那座克里斯達爾藝術館看一眼。", "name": "龍舌蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}, {"id": 311, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_lmstreet_2", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗚……", "name": "門板後的聲音"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎，你這是怎麼了？蹲在那裡哭一整天了。", "name": "門板後的聲音"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我一整天都很倒楣……今天遇見了很奇怪的移調譜，我拿的明明是小號的譜子，上面為什麼有低音譜號啊？作曲的人到底怎麼想的？", "name": "門板後的聲音"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "開始排練的時候，我突然想起譜子上有個好長的大空拍，中間就夾著幾個音。", "name": "門板後的聲音"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "上面有提示小音符嗎？", "name": "門板後的聲音"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有……等我數到的時候，才發現自己中間數錯了，進的時候快了。", "name": "門板後的聲音"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是一個非常響亮的強音，所有人都停下來看我……為什麼啊？作曲的人是不是根本不知道小號的譜怎麼寫啊？", "name": "門板後的聲音"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，這……休息一下，明天會好的……", "name": "門板後的聲音"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真的嗎……？", "name": "門板後的聲音"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_ltalley", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "明天我們的藝術節就要正式開始了……嘶，感覺有點緊張。", "name": "窗戶裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果你睡不著的話，可以起來幫我改下稿子嗎？", "name": "窗戶裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的稿子不是早就畫完了嗎？", "name": "窗戶裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是，但是昨天收尾的時候程式卡了，等它緩衝的時候我去吃了個晚飯，等我回來的時候，它就……", "name": "窗戶裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊啊啊——！等等，說到這裡就夠了，不要再說下去了！", "name": "窗戶裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "住口啊！", "name": "窗戶裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等啊——！你抱頭的動作小一點，我的板子在你手邊啊！！", "name": "窗戶裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$glass", "volume": 0.3}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒了……什麼都沒了……我今天怎麼這麼倒楣啊……", "name": "窗戶裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_ltalley", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$mist_intro", "key": "$mist_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_soldiersrun"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1272_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.5}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "報告，狙擊弩手已經佔領高處，無人發現。", "name": "全副武裝的軍人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1272_1#1$1"}, {"id": 362, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等待指令中。", "name": "全副武裝的軍人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1272_1#1$1"}, {"id": 363, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "48_g8_slums", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊哈……這一整天忙得要死，幾點了？好，還有點時間，去市裡喝一杯。", "name": "社區居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1"}, {"id": 375, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎喲——！", "name": "社區居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1"}, {"id": 377, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誰這麼沒有公德心啦，在路上放這麼大一塊石頭！", "name": "社區居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1"}, {"id": 378, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘶……今天是怎麼了？喝冷水也塞牙縫，明天得去找占卜師好好算一卦，轉轉運。", "name": "社區居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1"}, {"id": 379, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1216_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先生，不好意思，請回去，現在禁止外出。", "name": "整裝的軍人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1216_1#1$1"}, {"id": 385, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你誰啊？憑什麼攔我？", "name": "社區居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1"}, {"id": 387, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1216_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請回去，先生。", "name": "整裝的軍人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1216_1#1$1"}, {"id": 389, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喂，你們在做什麼？誰派你們來的？", "name": "社區居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1"}, {"id": 391, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1216_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請不要靠近，先生。", "name": "整裝的軍人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1216_1#1$1"}, {"id": 393, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_soldiersrun"}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.5}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很快，越來越多的身著制服的軍人從各個街道湧現，站在社區外，面色嚴峻，手中拿著武器。"}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幾輛漆成黑色的卡車從他們中間駛過，捲起了幾道灰塵。"}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們訓練有素地將車上的東西卸下，即使天色已經開始變得昏暗，但那東西足夠刺眼。"}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在所有人眼前，一捲捲帶著尖刺的鐵絲網鋪展開來，將整個社區包圍。"}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……你們……到底要來幹什麼？", "name": "社區居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1"}, {"id": 403, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1216_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先生，只是一次例行的消防檢查，您不必驚慌。", "name": "整裝的軍人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1216_1#1$1"}, {"id": 405, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "希望大家能配合我們的工作，我們將……感激不盡。", "name": "整裝的軍人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1216_1#1$1"}, {"id": 406, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}